---
title: Smart Saganaki-Style Tilapia  with Oregano Roasted Veggies
description: Mediterranean vibes abound in this healthy meal – it's filled with tilapia, eggplant, potatoes, tomatoes, feta and our secret ingredient, fresh oregano!
